"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-news-uk-1930054-tom-daley-granparents-olympic-gold-medal\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  The grandparents of British diver Tom Daley say they still get \\\"butterflies\\\" watching him dive but they 'could not be prouder' after watching him win his final Olympic medal.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 176, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 22, \"end\": 29, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.6048421106175182, \"rank\": 0.5643434798710287, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 36, \"end\": 45, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.284466202942071e-46, \"text\": \"Tom Daley\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Daley, 30, won his fifth Olympic medal after securing a silver alongside Noah Williams, 24, in the men's synchronised 10m platform in Paris on Monday morning.\", \"from\": 178, \"to\": 336, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 251, \"end\": 264, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Williams_(diver)\", \"score\": 0.999998273608197, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Williams\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Williams_(diver)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Williams_(diver)\"}, {\"begin\": 312, \"end\": 317, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999994766502829, \"rank\": 5.233500496360373e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The diver came out of retirement after his son, Robbie, six, said he wanted to see his dad dive at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 338, \"to\": 450, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 386, \"end\": 392, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robbie_Jackson\", \"score\": 0.5715436687394937, \"rank\": 0.7489301535404882, \"text\": \"Robbie\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robbie_Jackson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robbie_Jackson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Daley's grandparents Rosemary and David Daley, both 76,- watched on at home in Plymouth, Devon and could not be prouder.\", \"from\": 452, \"to\": 572, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 531, \"end\": 539, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Plymouth\", \"score\": 0.9999661813299292, \"rank\": 3.279413909609875e-05, \"text\": \"Plymouth\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Plymouth\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Plymouth\"}, {\"begin\": 541, \"end\": 546, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Devon\", \"score\": 0.9999996587369551, \"rank\": 3.3483806928624227e-07, \"text\": \"Devon\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Devon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Devon\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"David said: \\\"We are highly delighted really.\", \"from\": 574, \"to\": 618, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We knew it would be a problem to beat the Chinese.\", \"from\": 620, \"to\": 671, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 663, \"end\": 670, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"score\": 0.9301050593493874, \"rank\": 0.07412564843306173, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think Tom dived much the same but it's just that the Chinese were that much better on the day.\", \"from\": 673, \"to\": 770, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 729, \"end\": 736, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"score\": 0.9301050593493874, \"rank\": 0.07412564843306173, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 774, \"to\": 883, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 884, \"to\": 960, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 961, \"to\": 993, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  \\\"If the Chinese had slipped up on the last dive it would have changed everything.\\\"\", \"from\": 994, \"to\": 1100, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1026, \"end\": 1033, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"score\": 0.9301050593493874, \"rank\": 0.07412564843306173, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rosemary says she still gets nervous watching her grandson dive.\", \"from\": 1102, \"to\": 1166, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She said: \\\"All the family are proud of him.\", \"from\": 1168, \"to\": 1211, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I get butterflies watching him.\", \"from\": 1213, \"to\": 1245, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have always done that.\\\"\", \"from\": 1247, \"to\": 1273, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The grandparents were delighted to spot Daley's young family supporting him in Paris.\", \"from\": 1275, \"to\": 1360, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1354, \"end\": 1359, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999994766502829, \"rank\": 5.233500496360373e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rosemary said: \\\"You could see him on the telly - little Robbie's eyes peeping over.\", \"from\": 1362, \"to\": 1445, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1418, \"end\": 1424, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robbie_Jackson\", \"score\": 0.5715436687394937, \"rank\": 0.7489301535404882, \"text\": \"Robbie\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robbie_Jackson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robbie_Jackson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I just hope he remembers it.\\\"\", \"from\": 1447, \"to\": 1477, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Rosemary and David said they know how proud Daley's late dad Robert would have been.\", \"from\": 1479, \"to\": 1563, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Robert died from a brain tumour, aged 40, just a few days after Daley's 17th birthday and the family remember fondly how much he loved to watch his son dive.\", \"from\": 1565, \"to\": 1722, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Rosemary said: \\\"It's a happy sad story.\", \"from\": 1724, \"to\": 1763, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When Robert wasn't so well and we knew it was coming to the end he wanted to watch him in China for one day.\", \"from\": 1765, \"to\": 1874, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1856, \"end\": 1861, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9950259641552043, \"rank\": 0.004385785219597052, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I remember one time we were at Stratford watching him.\", \"from\": 1876, \"to\": 1931, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1908, \"end\": 1917, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stratford-upon-Avon\", \"score\": 0.9999998877294792, \"rank\": 1.1217065381164004e-07, \"text\": \"Stratford\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stratford-upon-Avon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stratford-upon-Avon\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"By then Robert was in a wheelchair.\", \"from\": 1932, \"to\": 1967, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But when he won something everyone stood up - he said 'quick help me up'.\", \"from\": 1969, \"to\": 2043, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He would insist on standing.\", \"from\": 2045, \"to\": 2074, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"What Robert did for Tom, I can see Tom doing it for his children.\", \"from\": 2076, \"to\": 2142, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He's a really good dad.\", \"from\": 2144, \"to\": 2168, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He would not be pushy with them.\", \"from\": 2170, \"to\": 2203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Robert wasn't pushy.\", \"from\": 2204, \"to\": 2224, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He would sit and watch and he'd be dead quiet.\", \"from\": 2226, \"to\": 2273, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He was the one who took him everywhere and made sure he had water.\\\"\", \"from\": 2275, \"to\": 2343, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"David said: \\\"Tom's fame is a result of Robert's work.\\\"\", \"from\": 2345, \"to\": 2399, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The doting grandparents also praised Daley's diving partner.\", \"from\": 2401, \"to\": 2461, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Rosemary said: \\\"He's lucky really he's got a partner with Noah because to find a partner to pair with Tom to replace Matty [Matty Lee] - hats off to Noah.\", \"from\": 2463, \"to\": 2617, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2521, \"end\": 2525, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah\", \"score\": 0.8260146443299657, \"rank\": 0.18731127593481195, \"text\": \"Noah\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah\"}, {\"begin\": 2587, \"end\": 2596, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matty_Lee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Matty Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matty_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matty_Lee\"}, {\"begin\": 2612, \"end\": 2616, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah\", \"score\": 0.8260146443299657, \"rank\": 0.18731127593481195, \"text\": \"Noah\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"David added: \\\"He's got to take as much of the credit because it takes two to do that.\\\"\", \"from\": 2619, \"to\": 2705, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SEARCH  CONNECT WITH US  TODAY'S PAPER  See today's front and back pages, download the newspaper, order back issues and use the historic Daily Express newspaper archive.\", \"from\": 2707, \"to\": 2876, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2844, \"end\": 2857, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.712865591480688e-21, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"EXPRESS.CO.UK  Daily Express uses notifications to keep you updated\", \"from\": 2878, \"to\": 2945, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2893, \"end\": 2906, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.712865591480688e-21, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}]}"